"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1930996-olympic-games-most-emotional-moments-history\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The Olympic Gamesrepresent the pinnacle of athletic achievement.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 66, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is so much pressure, high expectations and unbelievable comebacks which often leave us reduced to tears.\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A good part of the games which makes it so addictive are the stories.\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, we have delved into the lives of athletes from around the world and their personal narratives.\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stories of coming back from injury, returning from retirement, tales of struggle and strength - the list goes on.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics have produced a plethora of emotional moments which have kept us glued to the television screen.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember - these are the Olympic Games and leaving empty-handed is part and parcel of the world of professional sports.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not everyone will be victorious.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are ten emotional stories that have come from the history of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gemma Gibbons's London 2012 message  British judoka Gemma Gibbons shot to stardom not for her silver medal in London 2012, but for famously making the entire nation cry during her semi-final.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemma_Gibbons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gemma Gibbons\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemma_Gibbons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemma_Gibbons\"}, {\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1473705349735107e-17, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.6714333672985481, \"rank\": 0.4257158095287524, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemma_Gibbons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gemma Gibbons\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemma_Gibbons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemma_Gibbons\"}, {\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1473705349735107e-17, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After making it to the final, she broke into tears as she looked to the heavens, mouthing the words: \\\"I love you Mum.\\\"\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was sending a message to her mother who passed away in 2004 after suffering from leukaemia.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Muhammad Ali lights the cauldron in Atlanta  It's not just the sporting events that can leave us grabbing the tissues.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource