nclude adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 4743, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Austrian-German weightlifter Mattias Steiner lost his wife in a car accident in 2007, but this did not prevent him from competing in the 2008 Olympics.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He ended up winning the gold medal and later stood on the medalists' podium with a photo of his late wife.\", \"from\": 4953, \"to\": 5059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn't a dry eye in the house.\", \"from\": 5060, \"to\": 5096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5235, \"end\": 5248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.081175417971097e-28, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5284, \"end\": 5297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.081175417971097e-28, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"